How to use the tool bar\
\
From left to right:\
\
Save button: Saves all the current players and their current points. Clicking the button opens a file chooser that allows the user to select where they want to save the file. \
\
Load button: Opens a file chooser to load the players from a previously saved game. \
\
Delete button: This button deletes the selected player from the game. \
\
Bet button: Places a bet for the selected player. Enter the amount to bet in the field to the right.\
\
Bet field: This is where the user enters the amount to bet. \
\
Roll button: Rolls the dice for the player, then the house, and shows the results.\
